Catharine Bond Hill,  B.A., M.A., ’85 Ph.D.









Catharine Bond Hill is managing director of Ithaka S&R, Ithaka Harbors. For the past ten years, Ms. Hill served as president of Vassar College. She is a noted economist, whose research focuses on the affordability of and access to higher education, as well as on economic development and reform in Africa.
